    "about.subtitle": "An IT, AI & automation team for growing businesses",
    "about.title": "We build the systems your business actually runs on.",
    "about.p1": "<strong>Neurowaves</strong> designs and delivers technology for B2B, services, manufacturing, hospitality, and e-commerce — AI chat and voice bots, CRM implementation, custom internal systems, websites and web apps, Google promotion and SEO, data dashboards, integrations, and generative AI for your brand. Not a lone bot or landing page off the shelf: tools wired into how your company really works.",
    "about.p2": "We start with analysis — where processes break, data gets lost, and teams lose time on manual work. Then we build, connect, and train. Our job is working infrastructure and automation; your team turns it into business outcomes.",
    "about.btn1": "Request a review", "about.btn2": "Browse the work",
    "academy.title": "Level up your team with practical AI",
    "academy.desc": "Full implementation isn't always step one. Often a focused, hands-on course is enough to put AI to work in daily operations — for leadership, staff, and creative teams.",
